body.text:
[Bold statement alert] If you're sick of blowing money on "testing" or burning through agencies & coaches, frustrated with ads not working as expected, I have news for you...

It is not a lucky coincidence that so many people are coming to us to turn poor-performing campaigns into better results than they've had in 5-10 years with ads. 

(I have people spending $50 per day, $300 per day,  and $20K+ per day...)

I'm talking about veterans running ads since 2010 coming to me and getting better results today than ever before...

As well as newer Entrepreneurs with great products or services coming to us after spending years and thousands of dollars with coaching programs and/or agencies with nothing to show for it besides a lot of great ideas, or a period of 6-12 months of great ads that seems like a thing of the past.

Well, I'm here to tell you that when you commit to the full Everlasting Ad™ S͟y͟s͟t͟e͟m͟ AND follow our guidance with situational tactical ads management, get ready to be surprised... 

I love it when we get clients coming on Zoom after finally launching an evergreen campaign turning $1 into $2 with wide open eyes and mouth... 

...saying, "I can't believe this is happening. Is this for real?" 

I just laugh and say, "I told you so." :-)

Once we get ads with positive ROI daily or weekly, we focus on slowly scaling ad sets and budgets or look at improving ad creative or funnel optimization (Modifying order bumps, upsells, follow up, etc.)

The next step we take totally depends on the situation...
-Sometimes it's ad sets, audiences, budgets, and Campaign Objectives.
-Sometimes it's focusing on the Everlasting Ad hook. 
-Sometimes it's the offer & funnel. 
-Sometimes it's the evergreen webinar or mini-webinar.
-Sometimes Performance Branding. (Cold and warm)

If you want to learn how the Everlasting Ad™ S͟y͟s͟t͟e͟m͟ applies to YOUR situation, watch the short video on the following page now: https://magicmakers.io/everlasting-ads

body.text:
There's a new 'Viral-Direct Response-Branding social media SUPER Ad' disrupting content marketers, direct response advertisers, and branding experts everywhere...

It is NO coincidence that we’ve had more businesses go from 6 to 7 figures or 7 to 8 figures over the past 12-24 months than the last 12 years we’ve been doing this... 

The algorithms have changed… 
AI is here…
Skepticism is at an all-time high…

People are spending way too much time pumping out content hoping it will bring in customers, not realizing the organic content game is a LONG game. 

People are wasting money with ‘ad testing hacks’ that only produce mediocre results.

When people follow the Everlasting Ad™ process they create ONE good social media SUPER AD that combines the 4 DNA strands of Direct Response, Viral Videos, Content Marketing, and Brand Advertising…

AKA: an Everlasting Ad™

Like David Ogilvy said, “The test of a good idea is how long it will last.”

We have a 3-Day Everlasting Flight Camp starting soon…

This Flight Camp is perfect for you if you are:
1. Having a tough time getting organic reach and you want to leverage your content with paid traffic, without burning through cash. 
2. Currently running ads but your results are inconsistent, and you want to build a predictable and stable system for growth...
3. Struggling with ad disapprovals and compliance changes (and even having your accounts shut down and banned)...
4. Constantly rebuilding your ad sets after a few days or a few weeks because of Ad Burnout...
5. Burning through agencies or consultants - nobody seems to be able to run ads at a profit for you...
6. You're an agency, consultant or freelancer and you’re either churning through clients or attracting nightmare clients who don't appreciate you.(In a nutshell: You would enjoy a few elite clients who CHERISH your services and are grateful to pay you the high fees you should be charging...)

Flight Camp Schedule: 
Pre-Flight: The DNA of the Everlasting Ad Method
Day 1: Evergreen Offer & Funnel Economics for 2024
Day 2: Ad Building Blocks & Formulas
Day 3: Ads Management Secrets (We use while spending $3.5 million per month generating $5 million every month in dozens of industries.)

about.text: Keith Krance helps businesses Launch ONE Good Ad that Runs 24/7-365 on Facebook, Instagram and YouTube, Turning Strangers into Customers and Building Brand Awareness Fast...

body.text:
In over 80% of my recent Everlasting Ad funnel evergreen overhauls, this is what we did:

1. Fix Offer. (Create a low-ticket offer if it works for their situation, create a webinar,  re-position their physical product, or something else. People think they have this right but they usually don't)
2. Fix their low-ticket funnel if they have one. (I’ve yet to see a low-ticket funnel we haven’t been able to improve in a measurable way. (Front-end pricing, better order bumps, more or LESS upsells, better video transitioning to higher ticket offers, and more...) 
3. Pull your ‘Magic’ out and create ONE Good Everlasting Ad™ designed for cold traffic that optimizes for Sales or Leads.
4. Start using Facebook’s new ads manager optimization features
5. Consolidate campaigns and ad sets using larger budgets in some cases. In others, we'll use many ad sets with very small budgets. 
6. Create at least $10/day Performance Branding campaigns for Warm and Cold audiences. (Cold branding is where you have to be very careful with wasting all the money spent on this tactic. Warm Performance Branding is the most important to get rolling right away and let time and repetition work its magic.) 

Wanna see a short training of me going through the 7-step process we're using to transform ad campaigns on Facebook, YouTube, and TikTok in 2024?

>> https://dwm.dominatewebmedia.com/7-step-webinar

*BTW- We're overseeing over $6 million per MONTH in ad spend with my coaching and agency clients in dozens of industries, with people spending $10/day to $100/day to $100,000+ per DAY, and everywhere in between.

**During this training I also show you 2 options to get personal help from me: 
1. One that literally costs $21/mo. with a 14-day trial and compares to other programs charging $100-$200/mo.
2. Another where we either manage your ads, or train you/your team, or we turn your pillar videos into Everlasting ads, or even meet in person and make magic together. 

Let's DO this. 
-Keith

-Facebook ads should NOT burn out after 1-2 weeks. With an ‘Everlasting Ad’ your performance should start IMPROVING after 3-7 days…

If you’re sick of low ROIs from ads and want something that can scale consistently… 

Something to give to your agency to make their job easier… 

Something that will immediately improve your ROAS and continue to pay you back for 2-3 years... 

...then get a deck of Ads Magic cards and formulas now. 

Let’s DO this.

body.text:
There's a new 'Viral-Direct Response-Branding social media SUPER Ad' disrupting content marketers, direct response advertisers, and branding experts everywhere...

It is NO coincidence that we’ve had more businesses go from 6 to 7 figures or 7 to 8 figures over the past 12-24 months than the last 12 years we’ve been doing this... 

The algorithms have changed… 
AI is here…
Skepticism is at an all-time high…

People are spending way too much time pumping out content hoping it will bring in customers, not realizing the organic content game is a LONG game. 

People are wasting money with ‘ad testing hacks’ that only produce mediocre results.

When people follow the Everlasting Ad™ process they create ONE good social media SUPER AD that combines the 4 DNA strands of Direct Response, Viral Videos, Content Marketing, and Brand Advertising…

AKA: an Everlasting Ad™

Like David Ogilvy said, “The test of a good idea is how long it will last.”

We have a 3-Day Everlasting Flight Camp you can join for just $1 dollar starting soon…

This Flight Camp is perfect for you if you are:
1. Having a tough time getting organic reach and you want to leverage your content with paid traffic, without burning through cash. 
2. Currently running ads but your results are inconsistent, and you want to build a predictable and stable system for growth...
3. Struggling with ad disapprovals and compliance changes (and even having your accounts shut down and banned)...
4. Constantly rebuilding your ad sets after a few days or a few weeks because of Ad Burnout...
5. Burning through agencies or consultants - nobody seems to be able to run ads at a profit for you...
6. You're an agency, consultant or freelancer and you’re either churning through clients or attracting nightmare clients who don't appreciate you.(In a nutshell: You would enjoy a few elite clients who CHERISH your services and are grateful to pay you the high fees you should be charging...)

Flight Camp Schedule: 
Pre-Flight: The DNA of the Everlasting Ad Method
Day 1: Evergreen Offer & Funnel Economics for 2024
Day 2: Ad Building Blocks & Formulas
Day 3: Ads Management Secrets (We use while spending $3.5 million per month generating $5 million every month in dozens of industries.)

about.text: Keith Krance helps businesses Launch ONE Good Ad that Runs 24/7-365 on Facebook, Instagram and YouTube, Turning Strangers into Customers and Building Brand Awareness Fast...

body.text:
[How to get ads to work with any budget TODAY] The cost of ads are NOT more expensive than 5 years ago - in some cases they are cheaper...

People are just more skeptical and have more choices & access to more information. 

Yes, some of the Targeting and some of the off-platform pixel data has been removed due to tighter privacy. 

The A.I. in the algorithms are better than ever before, but we're also starting with a broader audience than ever before. 

This is where the Everlasting Ad™ + Perpetual Cold & Warm Branding comes in. 

The problem is 99% of businesses running Conversion with Branding are getting it all wrong.

They're either: 
1. Burning through ad spend with nothing to show for it but big warm retargeting audiences that don't convert soon enough to cover costs. 
2. Running only Conversion campaigns and watching conversion costs go through the roof and ads burn out quickly. (Or, not getting them to work at all because their storytelling or offer isn't good enough) 

(I made a 19-min video going through this 3-level system you can watch with NO email required)

The keys to hitting the sweet spot of high ROI and getting a compounding effect of building audience without overspending are: 

1. Campaign Objectives for each level (1: Engagement, 2: Sales/Leads,  3: Brand Awareness  w/Frequency caps)
2. The Content. (Use the 2-1-2 setup)
3. Budgets for each level (Must be careful with the top level and keep it small!)
4. Audiences (Layered on top, stacked cold & warm in  middle, and stacked warm on bottom)
5. Frequency Cap Level 3 (This is key for winning their heart and moving into permanent memory)
6. CTAs

The problem is most leaders delegate ads or video, but the team isn't equipped with the right authentic messaging.

You get a message written by a direct response copywriter or an Ai-generated ad or script with no soul.

When the leader or founder contributes to the Everlasting Ad creation process, you create a message WITH soul, that anybody can turn into multiple ads that convert and train the Ai to find the perfect buyer...

...all while building goodwill and brand awareness along the way.

In over 80% of my recent Everlasting Ad funnel evergreen overhauls, this is what we did:

2. Fix their low-ticket funnel if they have one. (I’ve yet to see a low-ticket funnel we haven’t been able to improve in a measurable way. (Front-end pricing, better order bumps, more or LESS upsells, better video transitioning to higher ticket offers, and more...) 
3. Pull your ‘Magic’ out and create ONE Good Everlasting Ad™ designed for cold traffic that optimizes for Sales or Leads.
4. Start using Facebook’s new ads manager optimization features
5. Consolidate campaigns and ad sets using larger budgets in some cases. In others, we'll use many ad sets with very small budgets. 
6. Create at least $10/day Performance Branding campaigns for Warm and Cold audiences. (Cold branding is where you have to be very careful with wasting all the money spent on this tactic. Warm Performance Branding is the most important to get rolling right away and let time and repetition work its magic.)

body.text:
In over 80% of my recent Everlasting Ad funnel evergreen overhauls, this is what we did:

1. Fix Offer. (Create a low-ticket offer if it works for their situation, create a webinar,  re-position their physical product, or something else. People think they have this right but they usually don't)
2. Fix their low-ticket funnel if they have one. (I’ve yet to see a low-ticket funnel we haven’t been able to improve in a measurable way. (Front-end pricing, better order bumps, more or LESS upsells, better video transitioning to higher ticket offers, and more...) 
3. Pull your ‘Magic’ out and create ONE Good Everlasting Ad™ designed for cold traffic that optimizes for Sales or Leads.
4. Start using Facebook’s new ads manager optimization features
5. Consolidate campaigns and ad sets using larger budgets in some cases. In others, we'll use many ad sets with very small budgets. 
6. Create at least $10/day Performance Branding campaigns for Warm and Cold audiences. (Cold branding is where you have to be very careful with wasting all the money spent on this tactic. Warm Performance Branding is the most important to get rolling right away and let time and repetition work its magic.) 

Wanna see a short training of me going through the 7-step process we're using to transform ad campaigns on Facebook, YouTube, and TikTok in 2024?

>> https://dwm.dominatewebmedia.com/7-step-webinar

*BTW- We're overseeing over $6 million per MONTH in ad spend with my coaching and agency clients in dozens of industries, with people spending $10/day to $100/day to $100,000+ per DAY, and everywhere in between.

**During this training I also show you 2 options to get personal help from me: 
1. One that literally costs $21/mo. with a 14-day trial and compares to other programs charging $100-$200/mo.
2. Another where we either manage your ads, or train you/your team, or we turn your pillar videos into Everlasting ads, or even meet in person and make magic together. 

Let's DO this. 
-Keith

body.text:
[How to get ads to work with any budget TODAY] The cost of ads are NOT more expensive than 5 years ago - in some cases they are cheaper...

People are just more skeptical and have more choices & access to more information. 

Yes, some of the Targeting and some of the off-platform pixel data has been removed due to tighter privacy. 

The A.I. in the algorithms are better than ever before, but we're also starting with a broader audience than ever before. 

This is where the Everlasting Ad™ + Perpetual Cold & Warm Branding comes in. 

The problem is 99% of businesses running Conversion with Branding are getting it all wrong.

They're either: 
1. Burning through ad spend with nothing to show for it but big warm retargeting audiences that don't convert soon enough to cover costs. 
2. Running only Conversion campaigns and watching conversion costs go through the roof and ads burn out quickly. (Or, not getting them to work at all because their storytelling or offer isn't good enough) 

(I made a 19-min video going through this 3-level system you can watch with NO email required)

The keys to hitting the sweet spot of high ROI and getting a compounding effect of building audience without overspending are: 

1. Campaign Objectives for each level (1: Engagement, 2: Sales/Leads,  3: Brand Awareness  w/Frequency caps)
2. The Content. (Use the 2-1-2 setup)
3. Budgets for each level (Must be careful with the top level and keep it small!)
4. Audiences (Layered on top, stacked cold & warm in  middle, and stacked warm on bottom)
5. Frequency Cap Level 3 (This is key for winning their heart and moving into permanent memory)
6. CTAs

The problem is most leaders delegate ads or video, but the team isn't equipped with the right authentic messaging.

You get a message written by a direct response copywriter or an Ai-generated ad or script with no soul.

When the leader or founder contributes to the Everlasting Ad creation process, you create a message WITH soul, that anybody can turn into multiple ads that convert and train the Ai to find the perfect buyer...

...all while building goodwill and brand awareness along the way.

body.text:
[How to get ads to work with any budget TODAY] The cost of ads are NOT more expensive than 5 years ago - in some cases they are cheaper...

People are just more skeptical and have more choices & access to more information. 

Yes, some of the Targeting and some of the off-platform pixel data has been removed due to tighter privacy. 

The A.I. in the algorithms are better than ever before, but we're also starting with a broader audience than ever before. 

This is where the Everlasting Ad™ + Perpetual Cold & Warm Branding comes in. 

The problem is 99% of businesses running Conversion with Branding are getting it all wrong.

They're either: 
1. Burning through ad spend with nothing to show for it but big warm retargeting audiences that don't convert soon enough to cover costs. 
2. Running only Conversion campaigns and watching conversion costs go through the roof and ads burn out quickly. (Or, not getting them to work at all because their storytelling or offer isn't good enough) 

(I made a 19-min video going through this 3-level system you can watch with NO email required)

The keys to hitting the sweet spot of high ROI and getting a compounding effect of building audience without overspending are: 

1. Campaign Objectives for each level (1: Engagement, 2: Sales/Leads,  3: Brand Awareness  w/Frequency caps)
2. The Content. (Use the 2-1-2 setup)
3. Budgets for each level (Must be careful with the top level and keep it small!)
4. Audiences (Layered on top, stacked cold & warm in  middle, and stacked warm on bottom)
5. Frequency Cap Level 3 (This is key for winning their heart and moving into permanent memory)
6. CTAs

The problem is most leaders delegate ads or video, but the team isn't equipped with the right authentic messaging.

You get a message written by a direct response copywriter or an Ai-generated ad or script with no soul.

When the leader or founder contributes to the Everlasting Ad creation process, you create a message WITH soul, that anybody can turn into multiple ads that convert and train the Ai to find the perfect buyer...

...all while building goodwill and brand awareness along the way.

snapshot.link_description: The new Everlasting Ad™ + Perpetual Cold & Warm Branding machine.
